// Built-in oil brush definitions
// Each brush is a parameter template; actual strokes randomize around these values.
//
// Fields:
//   type: "flat" | "filbert" | "round" | "knife" | "custom"
//   weight: base stroke width multiplier
//   bristles: [min, max] bristle count
//   taper: [min, max] — 0 = rectangular, 1 = fully tapered
//   oval: [min, max] — filbert oval shape (1 = flat, <1 = rounded)
//   curveSway: [min, max] — how much the stroke curves
//   deplete: [min, max] — paint depletion along stroke
//   chaos: [min, max] — general noise/randomness
//   dryBrush: probability of dry brush gaps (0-1)
//   opacity: [min, max] base alpha
//   spacing: dot spacing along stroke (lower = denser)

